question: I am a producer and I registered as an Assister on Pennie.com now I cannot access my account.
text:
I am a producer and I registered as an Assister on Pennie.com now I cannot access my account. 
          
        
If you completed the Assister registration by accident you will not be able to claim either account. You must call Pennies dedicated producer line for assistance at 1-844-844-4440.
